pangomm: pangomm (C++ Bindings for Pango)
pangomm:
pangomm: Pango is a library for layout and rendering of text, with an emphasis
pangomm: on internationalization. Pango can be used anywhere that text layout
pangomm: is needed; however, most of the work on Pango was done using the GTK+
pangomm: widget toolkit as a test platform. Pango forms the core of text and
pangomm: font handling for GTK+-2.
pangomm:
pangomm: This package contains the GNOME C++ Bindings for the Pango library.
pangomm:
pangomm:
